OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA generally dry bright day with
OL,6,Fsome good sunny spells and becoming
OL,7,Fvery warm. Cloudy for the Western
OL,8,FIsles with mist patches, the cloud
OL,9,Fspreading east through the day.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA cloudy and murky evening in
OL,12,Fthe west with some mist and patchy
OL,13,Fdrizzle at first. Mainly dry around
OL,14,Fthe Moray Firth with some late bright
OL,15,Fthen clear spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
