OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FMainly dry with early
OL,6,Fmorning cloud soon burning off to
OL,7,Fleave a warm and sunny day. However
OL,8,Fstaying rather cloudy for western
OL,9,Fcoasts where the odd light shower is
OL,10,Fpossible.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,13,FPartly cloudy but warm with the risk
OL,14,Fof heavy and thundery outbreaks of
OL,15,Frain on Thursday and Friday. Turning
OL,16,Ffresher by Saturday with the risk of a
OL,17,Ffew showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
